<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1915-11-19T17:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1915-11-19T17:00:00-05:00" n="1428" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1428">
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The</hi>
                            <gloss type="from">
                                <hi rend="italic">Secretary of State</hi>
                            </gloss>
                            <hi rend="italic">to the Minister in Persia</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_CJL1" type="to"><hi rend="italic">Caldwell</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-11-19T17:00:00-05:00">
                                    <hi rend="italic">November 19, 1915, 5 p. m.</hi>
                                </date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>Your November 17, 3 p. m. Department approves your assuming temporary
                            charge German and Turkish interests subject to approval of those
                            Governments. Please keep Department fully informed regarding situation.
                            You will use the greatest care and discretion in extending protection to
                            nationals other than Americans citizens.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <persName corresp="#p_LR1">
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                                </persName>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>